  "body": "**Steps to reproduce:**\r\n1. Create a new 1-1 chat\r\n2. Start typing text within a chat\r\n3. Tap 'back' button\r\n4. Open current chat again\r\n5. Try to edit the message saved into textbox\r\n6. Send the message\r\n\r\n**Actual result:**\r\n- The textbox does not react on the taps after step 5 and as result, the text can't be edited\r\n- The sent message is not visible fully after step 6 even after scrolling to the bottom\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/52490791/207652663-0470b84f-6d83-4a0e-b05a-ef9f91c25d40.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected result:**\r\n- Message is able to be edited after the user reopens the chat\r\n- The last sent message is visible and a user can't see it fully\r\n\r\n**ENV:** Huawei p20 light. v9\r\n\r\n**ADDITIONAL INFO:**\r\nThis issue is reproducible only for my real device. I tried to reproduce it on the other androids with the same OS v9, but was unsuccessful",
